<li class='cover' id='bookCover_473846'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/473846.Can_You_Hear_the_Nightbird_Call_"><img alt="Can You Hear the Nightbird Call?" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1320435935l/473846._SX98_.jpg" />
